<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #6750A4;
      --secondary: #625B71;
      --surface: #FEF7FF;
      --on-surface: #1D1B20;
      --outline: #79747E;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      font-family: "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
      background-color: #EADDFF;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    #render-target {
      background-color: var(--surface);
      color: var(--on-surface);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 24px;
      width: 500px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--secondary);
      margin-top: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .code-box {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .params-list {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .param-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .param-name {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--primary);
      min-width: 80px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--outline);
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--outline);
      text-align: right;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="render-target">
    <div class="title">PJSK 贴纸生成器帮助</div>
    
    <div class="section-title">使用方法:</div>
    <div class="code-box">/pjsk &lt;角色名&gt; &lt;文本内容&gt; [参数]</div>
    
    <div class="section-title">可选参数:</div>
    <div class="params-list">
      <div class="param-item"><span class="param-name">pos=(x,y)</span> <span>文本位置</span></div>
      <div class="param-item"><span class="param-name">clr=(r,g,b)</span> <span>文本颜色</span></div>
      <div class="param-item"><span class="param-name">fs=大小</span> <span>字体大小</span></div>
      <div class="param-item"><span class="param-name">font=字体</span> <span>字体类型</span></div>
      <div class="param-item"><span class="param-name">rot=角度</span> <span>旋转角度</span></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section-title">示例:</div>
    <div class="code-box">/pjsk miku 你好</div>
    <div class="code-box">/pjsk rin 测试 pos=(50,50) clr=(255,0,0)</div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      Generated by AmiaBot<br>
      Designed by Parallel SEKAI
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
